snippet.title: HYPERFATAL - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
HYPERFATAL is a fast-paced old school FPS that combines the explosive action of movement shooters with unique mechanics similar to Quake and popular Source engine games.

Wishlist On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2903590/HyperFatal/

Join our Discord (get notified for updates, participate in playtests, give feedback) https://discord.gg/MT3PB7EhdQ
